Recent Posts Sidebar Plugin for Typo

Created by Frédéric de Villamil
http://fredericdevillamil.com

A simple plugin that displays the last posts published in the sidebar.
You can choose the number of posts to display (default 10), and the length of the snippet (default 150).

Feel free to contact me for support or improvement : frederic@de-villamil.com.

This plugin is released under the MIT Licence.

Requirement : Typo v4.0 and above with plugins in the /vendor/plugins 

Install : just unpack this archive in your /vendor/plugins/ directory, restart your Typo, log in as an administrator and activate the plugin into the sidebar page. You're done.